@suharshs @karmel Thanks for replying. I'm getting the .pb file from the training script provided by Googlecodelabs/TensorFlow and is explained here. The CNN architecture I'm using is mobilenet_1.0_224_quantized. So, a quantised mobilenet model in .pb format is generated, I'm trying to convert it to .lite format and I'm running into that issue.

In particular your graph should include FakeQuant operations that store the quantization range information for TOCO.
How do I confirm if my graph has FakeQuant operations?
